<h2>Vegetable Biryani</h2>
<img src="images/biryani.jpg" alt="Biryani">
<p><strong>Prep Time:</strong> 60 mins | <strong>Difficulty:</strong> Hard</p>
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>Basmati rice, Mixed veg, Fried onions, Saffron, Spices</li></ul>
<h3>Steps</h3>
<ol><li>Parboil rice. <li>Cook veg gravy. <li>Layer and steam 20 mins.</ol>